# Maths and Physics Tuition



  - Highly qualified and experienced tutors
  - Online tutoring
  - Individual One-to-One or small group tuition in our tuition centre
  - Subjects covered - MATHS, FURTHER MATHS, APPLIED MATHS, PHYSICS
  - GCSE, IGCSE, or AS, A-Level for all major exam boards including AQA, Edexcel, OCR, and CIE
  
  
  
  
  
  
## Our Teaching Approach

  Our teaching approach is simple, but logical. Difficult theories by simple day to day examples-activities. If a student needs to get an excellent result at first time, this is the way to guarantee the success!
  
  - Individualized, Customized Learning Plans
  - Different Approaches to different students depending on their knowledge 
  - Special Exam Preparations through step-by-step guidance
  - Proven Success, grade improvement and higher test scores



